#: ../../source/index.rst:13
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "简介"

#: ../../source/index.rst:15
msgid ""
"This project is an automatic CVRP heuristic discovery framework based on "
"the **FunSearch** method. By combining Large Language Models (LLMs) with "
"evolutionary search, the framework generates high-performance CVRP "
"solvers without hand-crafted heuristic rules."
msgstr ""
"本项目是一个基于 **FunSearch** 方法的 CVRP 启发式算法自动发现框架。"
"通过结合大语言模型（LLM）与进化搜索，框架能够在无需人工设计启发式规则的情况下，"
"自动生成高性能的 CVRP 求解算法。"

#: ../../source/index.rst:20
msgid "Key Features"
msgstr "主要特性"

#: ../../source/index.rst:22
msgid ""
"**Automatic algorithm generation**: LLM iteratively generates candidate "
"algorithms"
msgstr "**自动算法生成**：LLM 迭代生成候选算法"

#: ../../source/index.rst:23
msgid "**Sample-efficient search**: early pruning reduces evaluation overhead"
msgstr "**样本高效搜索**：通过早期剪枝减少评估开销"

#: ../../source/index.rst:24
msgid ""
"**Functional equivalence detection**: avoids re-evaluating semantically "
"identical algorithms"
msgstr "**功能等价检测**：避免重复评估语义相同的算法"

#: ../../source/index.rst:25
msgid "**Multi-scale evaluation**: tests on small / medium / large instances"
msgstr "**多尺度评估**：在小/中/大规模实例上测试"

#: ../../source/index.rst:26
msgid "**Standard benchmarks**: supports CVRPLib benchmark datasets"
msgstr "**标准基准测试**：支持 CVRPLib 标准数据集"

